/* DO NOT REMOVE ANYTHING BELOW HERE WITHOUT ASKING JOHN HUDSON */

/* ----- HERO ----- */
.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed {
	margin: 0;
	overflow: hidden;
	padding: 0;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .s-container__inner,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .s-container__inner {
	max-width: 100%;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .widgettitle,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .widgettitle {
	display: block;
    margin: 45px auto 30px;
    max-width: 1440px;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item {
	padding: 0.5px;
	text-align: left;
  margin-bottom: 0!important;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:after,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:after {
	content: "";
	display: table;
	clear: both;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .entry-content,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .entry-content {
	display: block;
	padding: 30px 30px 65px 30px;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:first-child .entry-content,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:first-child .entry-content {
	background: rgb(82,21,120);
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(left,  rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 0%, rgba(33,109,181,0.8) 100%);
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left,  rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 0%,rgba(33,109,181,0.8) 100%);
	background: linear-gradient(to right,  rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 0%,rgba(33,109,181,0.8) 100%);
	border-radius: 5px 0 0 0;
	height: auto;
	left: unset;
    max-width: 720px;
    right: 0;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:last-child .entry-content,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item:last-child .entry-content {
	background: rgb(229,42,24);
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(left,  rgba(229,42,24,0.8) 0%, rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 100%);
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left,  rgba(229,42,24,0.8) 0%,rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 100%);
	background: linear-gradient(to right,  rgba(229,42,24,0.8) 0%,rgba(82,21,120,0.8) 100%);
	border-radius: 0 5px 0 0;
	height: auto;
    max-width: 720px;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item h3, 
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item h3{
	height: 120px;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item h3 span,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item h3 span {
	background: none;
	box-shadow: none;
	color: white;
	line-height: 1;
	padding: 0;
	text-shadow: 1px 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .taxonomy-signpost,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .taxonomy-signpost {
	background: #000000;
	border-radius: 20px;
	bottom: 30px;
	color: #ffffff;
	display: block;
	font-size: 0.65em;
	left: 28px;
	padding: 5px 10px;
    position: absolute;
    text-transform: capitalize;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author,
.listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .date {
	color: #ffffff;
	float: left;
	margin: 30px 0 0 0;
    padding-right: 10px;
    text-transform: capitalize;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author {
	margin-right: 10px;
	padding-right: 12px;
	position: relative;
}

.home .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author:after,
.page .listing--hero.s-container--fullbleed .listing-item .author:after {
	background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
	content: '';
	height: 10px;
	position: absolute;
	top: 3px;
	right: 1px;
    width: 1px;
}

/* ----- SINGLE INC SIDEBAR / FILMSTRIP ----- */

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar,
.home .listing--filmstrip,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar,
.page .listing--filmstrip {
  background: #eef4fa;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0 15px;
}

.home .listing--filmstrip,
.page .listing--filmstrip {
	padding-bottom: 15px;
}

.home .listing--filmstrip p,
.page .listing--filmstrip p {
	color: #55627e;
}

.home .listing--filmstrip-b p,
.page .listing--filmstrip-b p {
	color: #ffffff;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .widgettitle,
.home .listing--filmstrip .widgettitle,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .widgettitle,
.page .listing--filmstrip .widgettitle {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1440px;
    padding: 30px 0 15px 0;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-items,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-items {
  padding: 15px 0;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-item,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-item {
  margin: 0;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry {
  border-bottom: 1px #ffffff solid;
  display: flex;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  padding-bottom: 15px;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-item:last-child .listing-entry,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-item:last-child .listing-entry {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-image,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-image {
  padding-top: 60%;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-media,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-media {
  flex-basis: 30%;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content {
  flex-basis: 70%;
  padding: 0 15px;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content h3,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content h3 {
  font-size: 0.8em
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost,
.home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost,
.page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost {
  background: #000000;
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 0.6em;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  padding: 2px 5px;
  text-transform: capitalize;
}


.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author,
.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .date,
.home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author,
.home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .date,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .date,
.page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author,
.page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .date {
  color: #55627e;
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.6em;
  margin: 0;
  text-transform: capitalize;
}

.home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .querywidget-more,
.page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .querywidget-more {
  margin: 0;
  padding-bottom: 15px;
}

@media( min-width: 992px) {
  /* ----- SINGLE INC SIDEBAR ----- */
	
	.home .listing--filmstrip,
  .page .listing--filmstrip {
		padding-bottom: 30px;
	}

  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-media,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-media {
      flex-basis: 25%;
  }
  
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry h3,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry h3 {
      font-size: 1.2em;
			padding-bottom: 0px;
  }
  
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-content,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-content {
      display: block;
  }
  
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost, 
  .home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost, 
  .page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .taxonomy-signpost {
    font-size: 0.8em;
  }


  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author,
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .date,
  .home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author,
  .home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .date,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .date,
  .page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author,
  .page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .date {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8em;
    margin-right: 10px;
    padding-right: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author:after,
  .home .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author:after,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .entry-content .author:after,
  .page .listing--filmstrip .entry-content .author:after {
    background: #a6acbb;
    content: '';

    position: absolute;
    right: -2px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 1px;
  }
  
  .home .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-image,
  .page .listing--single-inc-sidebar .listing-entry .entry-image {
      padding-top: 56.25%;

.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container {
  border-top: 3px solid transparent;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
  border-image: linear-gradient(to right, #E52A18 0%, #521578 100%) 1;
  min-width: 100%;
  margin: 20px 0;
  padding: 15px 0 25px 0;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list h3.egl-combo-title {
  display: block;
  margin: 0 0 20px 0;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track:not(:first-of-type) {
    margin-top: 12px;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a {
  border-radius: 5px;
  background-color: white;
  height: 90px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  position: relative;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div:nth-child(2) {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 10px 0 0 10px;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div:nth-child(2) div.egl-deal-stock {
  display: none;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-name {
  overflow: hidden;
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-price {
    display: flex;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-name,
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-price {
  color: #000;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: bold;
  line-height: 16px;
  align-items: center;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div:nth-child(2),
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-price {
  height: 45px;
  background-color: #EEF4FA;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-price {
  justify-content: flex-end;
  padding: 10px 15px 0 0;
  color: #E52A18;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-logo,
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-view {

  bottom: 0;
  flex: 1;
  height: 45px;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-logo {
  left: 0;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track a div.egl-deal-view {

  border-top-left-radius: 5px;
  background-color: white;

  border: 1px solid white;
  border-radius: 5px;
  position: absolute;
  right: 15px;
  bottom: 20px;
  flex: 1;
  margin-right: 0;
  height: 30px;
  width: 80px;
}
.eagle-widget.eagle-combo-widget .egl-combo-container .egl-combo-list div.egl-combo-row.egl-track:first-of-type a div.egl-deal-view .egl-tr-button {
  color: white;
